\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10175054\charrsid12455492 Oh, I liked it all right, it wa
s a nice easy job, especially in the buttery, I had to do the serving, they, the waiters used to come, you see, to ..}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 So they were nice to you there in the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Yes, oh yes, they were very nice indeed, oh yes, comfortable it were a lovely job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 How did you get hold of it? How did you come to hear of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 My bro-, my eldest brother worked there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Full time, did he work there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 No, only, no only in term, only in term.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 When you went in to do the printing work, the printer's devil, how did you find that work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 
Well, I liked it all right, you know, because there was a, boys like myself there, and the men were decent, so I was always quite comfortable in a way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 And how did you get hold of that work? How did you come to hear about that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 I just called on the chance (..) ask them if they needed a boy
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Was that before you left school you started looking, or after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Af-, no after, yes I'd left school. I remember wandering round the town depr
essed as anybody could be, miserable because I had nothing to do. I'd been so busy all of my life, it was being out of work and all, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14550504\charrsid12455492 my}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492  money a term such as it was, was only five shillings, that was five shillings. I'll tell you one thing that always struc
k me very forcibly. I'd seen my poor old mother, no money to get any food for us, and she'd take her purse out, you know, bit agitated, and shake it as if she could shake out another penny, well, (..) \{BLANK\}
 And I'll tell you what made me turn a Socialist}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14550504\charrsid12455492 ,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492  being a freeman I should be a Conservative really but, I've seen boys when 
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10175054\charrsid12455492 I went to school at St. Thomas\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 , that's by the church, that, our school not this one over }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10175054\charrsid12455492 here,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492  I've seen one or two boys before they went into school at nine o'clock go round this back yard, you, you don't know this place, do you?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 I've never been here before till today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 All this is, i-, i-, it comes in a square, right round, well, er, in between, you see all the backs of these buildings, except mine}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10175054\charrsid12455492 , this don\rquote t happen to come}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 
 'cause it's a corner house. It was a big back yard with all the lines for the different people (..) \{BLANK\} grass cutting, I've seen everything, and the people who lived in the back, they, if they had, might have some, er, stale bread, and they'd c
huck the stale bread in pieces to the birds on to the grass, you see. Two of the boys used to come out early, pick up that bread and eat it, 'cause they'd got nothing to eat to go to school, and when I realised that the thought, I thought to myself, well,
 England is suppo-, supposed to, well, she was, the most powerful and the richest country in the world, and yet they, nothing could be done. Why not? They (..) \{BLANK\}
 in trouble, and I tried to be a Socialist, and have been every since. They're for workers.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 About how old were you when you remember seeing those boys eating bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Well, anything from about, er, nine to, er, when I left school, thirteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Oh, quite a young boy when you thought about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Oh, yes (..) too hard for the people to eat as }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10175054\charrsid12455492 bread about}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492  here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 
And then, when you got these ideas that things should be changed, how did you actually find out about Socialism? How do you remember first hearing about the theory of Socialism and this kind of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Well, I read it in the papers, you see, oh yes I see one point of view, I mean I read papers even then because I was always very}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10175054\charrsid12455492 , }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 very interested in reading.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Did your mother and father have a paper in the house? a daily paper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Dad was illiterate. He couldn't read; he couldn't write, but he was a shrewd man, I can tell you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Did you ever read to him? Did anyone ever read to him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10175054\charrsid12455492 Never thought of it, too noisy at home too crowded, you see, in the house.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10175054\charrsid12455492 How did you manage to find a place to read then where you could learn things from?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 I don't know, I used to just, it would have been at bedtime you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 You mean, in bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Used to take a book, used to take a book to bed, wake up at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname time}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour}
