 before I was married, but, yes, he did, he did take us out sometimes, with mother. We'd sometimes go down, for instance, from here, to, er, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2441644\charrsid12455492 Hunksey}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
