\insrsid2441644\charrsid12455492 Bittery}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492  Road (talking together here)
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Well, you can walk, go up (..) \{ILLEGIBLE\} just over by the (..) \{ILLEGIBLE\} Church, just as you get there, that's (..) \{ILLEGIBLE\}
