\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 But even so, it was pretty tough. What sort of thing would you have to do}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12455492  }{\rtlch\fcs1 
