\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Yes, If you was late, stood in, you didn't go in y
