\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Practically, yes, all poorish people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 No tradespeople's sons, or that kind of person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 No, no, Not one.
