\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 From seventeen to twenty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 That's it. Three years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 What did you do, then between thirteen and seventeen? I thought that was when you were the printer's devil.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Oh, well, I, I was, er, I was at, er, in the college, you see. (Rather muffled here).
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Oh, I'm sorry I didn't get it quite clear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 When you left school then, you had that job in the buttery?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Was that full time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 No. That's why had to have, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 That's why you said you were depressed, because you didn't have enough work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 That's right, ye-.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 I got that wrong, I thought you were doing the buttery job while you were still at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Ah, now, I was doing the hall door, if you remember.
