ferent job. I served stuff out, you see, to the waiters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 I remember you telling me that. I'd just got the ages wrong. So you did that from when you left school till you were seventeen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4789066 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 That's right, yes.
