rint. He said, look (?), ha-, have a go on this, he said, it's all made ready, the chief part of printing, is making it ready, getting it ready, it's all ready, he said, watch how you go, oh, oh, I could do that, I says, Mr. (..) Butler that gave me a sta
rt, you see.
