\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11555284 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14181748\charrsid12455492 Were there any set times, a set time she used to buy clothes or just ..?
